data.description: Huge Reduction over $100,000!   This high-end charmer has an elevator, large covered pool, sunroom, ground source heat pump and Dixie REA for low utilities.  Workshop, lots of covered parking, RV parking. Basement apartment, 2nd story studio, both with exterior entrances.  Laundry hookups on each level, hidden basement storage, large attic bonus room.  Pressurized irrigation water, hidden cargo container, little pirate cave, zipline to pool, tree house and so many other things to make this a fun, unique property you have to see.  I cannot do it justice!  This was a grandpa making a resort for his grandkids.  Such a great property!
